│ very first proposed solution from the root cause analysis.   │
│                                                              │
│ The correct fix is to guard the `foldAndOrOfICmps`           │
│ optimization by checking if either of the `ICmpInst`         │
│ operands has the `samesign` property, using the public       │
│ `isSameSign()` method. The initial failures with this        │
│ approach were likely due to transient environment issues or  │
